      "solution": "s = input()\n\ndef decrypt(s):\n    words = s.split()\n    n = len(words)\n    crypted_words = [words[i-1][-1] + w[1:-1] + words[(i+1)%n][0] for i, w in enumerate(words)]\n    return ' '.join(crypted_words)\n\nprint(decrypt(s))",
